    "name": "GHUNTER",
    "steam_appid": 3156000,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become <strong>Ghunter</strong>, a gnome chef that will create dishes by cooking creatures... <strong>ALIVE!!</strong> Use your various cooking based weapons to cook your prey alive and brutally finish them off with your multi-purpose melee weapon! Ghunter has the responsability to <strong>save the King</strong> by providing dishes to his servants and other characters to heal him.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>FEATURES</strong></u><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156000/extras/1aacb3a302ab1d86720842bb5b5d1d12.avif?t=1736967989\" width=600 height=167 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlike other games, GHUNTER <strong>fuses</strong> the process of hunting and cooking in one. Use your multiple culinary-inspired equipment to create different delicious dishes!   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156000/extras/64b059ce2731618ff16faaefc3e5006f.poster.avif?t=1736967989\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156000/extras/64b059ce2731618ff16faaefc3e5006f.webm?t=1736967989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156000/extras/64b059ce2731618ff16faaefc3e5006f.mp4?t=1736967989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156000/extras/7a98e3cf85f5a94ad6256648f6690564.avif?t=1736967989\" width=600 height=167 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game provides with an interesting and intricate narrative driven by charismatic characters with a dynamic narrative system where your dialogue choices matter. Unveil the mysteries of Gernik by finding lore inside the adventure. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156000/extras/685be10890f2d70a83499c754e862bec.poster.avif?t=1736967989\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156000/extras/685be10890f2d70a83499c754e862bec.webm?t=1736967989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156000/extras/685be10890f2d70a83499c754e862bec.mp4?t=1736967989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156000/extras/cc412d5cf39e1f10fc96510211217988.avif?t=1736967989\" width=600 height=167 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >By finding different items in the adventure and completing customer orders, you will have the ability to upgrade Ghunter's equipment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156000/extras/99f90c9fac4865bd4e12b2f089b12e40.poster.avif?t=1736967989\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156000/extras/99f90c9fac4865bd4e12b2f089b12e40.webm?t=1736967989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156000/extras/99f90c9fac4865bd4e12b2f089b12e40.mp4?t=1736967989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156000/extras/1bed3739d0fd634f3b7d1daf0017a531.avif?t=1736967989\" width=600 height=167 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >GHUNTER's tavern is equipped with a order board where he will be able to pick up dishes to the player's choosing. Once completed, you will submit it to gain satisfaction of said customer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156000/extras/cffc85cbddc1af184fe604f44f0e7667.poster.avif?t=1736967989\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156000/extras/cffc85cbddc1af184fe604f44f0e7667.webm?t=1736967989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156000/extras/cffc85cbddc1af184fe604f44f0e7667.mp4?t=1736967989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156000/extras/97738ab313f73423af306a257add2aed.avif?t=1736967989\" width=600 height=167 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Despite looking so colourful and pretty, the world of Gernik is more unsettling than it meets the eye. Both the narrative and the cooking have a dark side.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156000/extras/892424c5c90225fa1dbb3e3dddcb56c1.avif?t=1736967989\" width=600 height=167 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unveil the secrets of the world. Discover portals, landmarks, statues, chests and much more! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156000/extras/e656a5605f88b578674429ce381b139b.poster.avif?t=1736967989\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156000/extras/e656a5605f88b578674429ce381b139b.webm?t=1736967989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156000/extras/e656a5605f88b578674429ce381b139b.mp4?t=1736967989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156000/extras/9019ce9584e56ac4389068a96a9152fa.avif?t=1736967989\" width=600 height=167 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Check all your progress and unlocks in the adventure book. Here you can see  the world map, lore entries, creature descriptions, recipes and more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156000/extras/8da6a4ddecb13cb688c8f55334ceb0c1.poster.avif?t=1736967989\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156000/extras/8da6a4ddecb13cb688c8f55334ceb0c1.webm?t=1736967989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156000/extras/8da6a4ddecb13cb688c8f55334ceb0c1.mp4?t=1736967989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>More about this game</strong></u><br><br>Game developped as a  final project of the Art, Design and Programming masters of the U-tad university of Madrid, Spain. This project mixed all 3 of those departments with the help of other masters such as concept art, 3D modelers, animators and rigging.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156000/extras/62dac3ecf0d0b87a98cb0a64ef05427d.avif?t=1736967989\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156000/extras_big/62dac3ecf0d0b87a98cb0a64ef05427d.avif?t=1736967989 width=800 height=385 /></span></p>",
